So for the first 20
minutes, 25 minutes

00:12:06.690 --> 00:12:08.970
of class, what
I'd like you to do

00:12:08.970 --> 00:12:10.980
is I'd like you to
pretend that you

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:15.240
were part of a department,
the STEM department.

00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:18.500
Call it whatever field you want.

00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:20.900
